## **ðŸŽ¨ Styling Highlights (CSS)**

```css
/* Highlight the currently playing song */
.playlist-song.active {
    background-color: #1db954;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

/* Progress bar */
.progress-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

.progress-bar {
    flex: 1;
    height: 5px;
    background: #444;
    border-radius: 5px;
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin: 0 10px;
}

.progress {
    height: 100%;
    width: 0%;
    background: #1db954;
    border-radius: 5px;
}
```

